data.description: Welcome to LAKE ARROWHEAD LIVING! This charming residence features 4 BEDROOMS and 3 BATHROOMS, providing ample space for both comfort and versatility. The thoughtful design includes a IN-LAW SUITE IN THE BASEMENT, complete with a separate entrance for added privacy and convenience. The basement is a versatile space, perfect for extended family, guests, or even as a rental opportunity. 2 LOTS COBMINED TO MAKE IT A SPACIOUS 1 ACRE LOT! Step inside to discover a blend of warmth and functionality, with a floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. SPACIOUS FAMILY ROOM with vaulted ceiling and WARM wood burning FIREPLACE; SPLIT BEDROOM PLAN with large OWNERS SUITE on one side with UPDATED MASTER BATHROOM and 2 BEDROOMS with adjoining BATHROOM on the other side; The Upstairs LOFT AREA is a versatile space to use for office, playroom, workout etc. and plenty of storage; One of the highlights of this Lake Arrowhead home is the DECK, where you can immerse yourself in the beauty of mountain nature. Relax and unwind in the HOT TUB, taking in the tranquility of your surroundings. Whether it's morning coffee or evening stargazing, the deck provides a perfect vantage point to appreciate the natural beauty that surrounds you. LAKE ARROWHEAD offers a host of amenities for residents, including a pristine LAKE, GOLF COURSE, HIKING TRAILS, TENNIS and more. This home not only provides a comfortable haven but also grants access to a vibrant community and a lifestyle that embraces the great outdoors. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home, where the quiet cul-de-sac, wooded lot, and the enchanting seasonal lake views come together to create an unparalleled living experience in Waleska, GA. Embrace the tranquility and beauty of Lake Arrowhead living in this captivating 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom retreat.
